Description: # vtt2text
        
        [![vtt2text](https://img.shields.io/badge/repo-vtt2text-brightgreen)](https://github.com/vuanhtuan1012/vtt2text)
        ![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.6-blue.svg)
